        2. Description of Services
      </h2>
      <p>
        Pixelated Empathy provides a secure AI therapy platform designed
        specifically for mental health professionals. Our services include but
        are not limited to:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 my-4">
        <li>Secure, encrypted therapy communication and record-keeping</li>
        <li>
          AI-assisted therapy tools and insights using Fully Homomorphic
          Encryption (FHE)
        </li>
        <li>HIPAA-compliant client management and documentation tools</li>
        <li>Encrypted analytics and reporting features</li>
        <li>Secure client portals and communication channels</li>
      </ul>
