        We reserve the right to modify, suspend, or discontinue any part of our
        services at any time, with or without notice. We will make reasonable
        efforts to notify you of significant changes to the services.
      </p>

      <h2
        class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4"
        style="color: #4a9a95 !important;"
      >
        3. HIPAA Compliance and Business Associate Agreement
      </h2>
      <p>
        For healthcare providers subject to the Health Insurance Portability and
        Accountability Act of 1996 and its implementing regulations ("HIPAA"),
